# Phase 14 — workbook ingestion local override.
# The committed configs/workbook_v7_manifest.yaml is a SCAFFOLD with
# `<TODO_*>` placeholder sheet names. The user copies it to the
# `_local.yaml` variant, fills in real sheet names + row classification
# rules, and runs ingestion against the local file. The local variant
# is gitignored so live sheet identifiers and per-row classification
# detail never reach the repo.
configs/workbook_v7_manifest_local.yaml
configs/investment_summary_manifest_local.yaml
